  "3337130": {
    "name": "RMF's Ragdoll Physics Experiments",
    "steam_appid": 3337130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/400a6c0cc41c6080c93530fd03a9e34a.avif?t=1771935482\" width=902 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RMF’s Ragdoll Physics Experiments</strong> is a darkly humorous experience set inside an ever-sprawling research facility that’s held together by warning signs, far too many doors, and an AI voice that will absolutely <strong>judge</strong> you for everything you do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore interconnected rooms full of secrets, puzzles, and strange little discoveries. Then take what you’ve unlocked and turn it into <strong>glorious experimental physics based disasters</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>-------About the Demo-------</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the <strong>demo</strong>, you’ll play through the game’s <strong>onboarding sequence</strong> so you can get a proper feel for how the facility works. It introduces the <strong>core mechanics</strong>, the <strong>build-and-break</strong> sandbox, and of course the <strong>Voice of the Facility</strong>, your enthusiastic, sarcastic guide who is definitely taking notes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This demo will be <strong>evolving</strong> alongside the main game, so expect it to change and improve over time as we build towards release. If anything breaks, delights, or creates a brand new form of physics nonsense, please share your thoughts in the <strong>Steam Community Hub</strong> or jump into our <strong>Discord</strong> so we can keep shaping it with your <strong>feedback</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/986ce1147b796cb6983a6d1cb6142fa8.poster.avif?t=1771935482\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/986ce1147b796cb6983a6d1cb6142fa8.webm?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/986ce1147b796cb6983a6d1cb6142fa8.mp4?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or <strong>fire cannons</strong> first and then worry about the questions later.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/918ba00ba871dda24c4a0f4367dd3051.poster.avif?t=1771935482\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/918ba00ba871dda24c4a0f4367dd3051.webm?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/918ba00ba871dda24c4a0f4367dd3051.mp4?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/67e9b5fa30f1f033661836f66843e79f.avif?t=1771935482\" width=902 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the <strong>S.A.F.E. shop</strong> and unlock new <strong>gadgets</strong> to play with in the <strong>sandbox</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/5194fa70e66f6c176e02f7dba007fac7.poster.avif?t=1771935482\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/5194fa70e66f6c176e02f7dba007fac7.webm?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/5194fa70e66f6c176e02f7dba007fac7.mp4?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place traps, launchers, and props in Setup Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit <strong>GO</strong> to enter physics mode and watch it all unfold in beautiful slow-mo glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete tasks, earn stars, and unlock more gadgets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig into hidden rooms, unlock new toys, and try to figure out what the deal is with the <strong>overly talkative facility AI</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/631a073fab2e7b382a711b16d5a60cff.poster.avif?t=1771935482\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/631a073fab2e7b382a711b16d5a60cff.webm?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/631a073fab2e7b382a711b16d5a60cff.mp4?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/24af279ac8ee9166b14e66e3f898594b.avif?t=1771935482\" width=902 height=196 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge Rooms fuel the chaos</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenges and earn credits to spend in the <strong>S.A.F.E. shop</strong>, unlocking <strong>new gadgets</strong> like cannons, traps, hatches, springboards, and other <strong>problem-solving devices</strong> that are begging to be misused.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock props by recycling RPX cola bottles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Props are the <strong>chunky real-world stuff</strong>: furniture, appliances, heavy objects, and all the lovely clutter that makes physics fun. As you discover more, your sandbox grows in the most <strong>unhelpfully random</strong> way possible.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rescue new ragdolls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other <strong>ragdolls</strong> are scattered around the facility. Find them and you’ll have more “<strong>volunteers</strong>” for your experiments.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Setup Mode, then GO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your <strong>scenario</strong> by placing gadgets, props, and ragdolls. Then press <strong>GO</strong> to <strong>activate physics</strong> and enjoy the consequences. Reset, tweak, and watch it again in <strong>beautiful slow motion</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The facility has a personality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Voice of the Facility</strong> will passive-aggressively guide you as you go… but it definitely feels like <strong>something bigger is going on</strong> behind the walls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/f645674066f538bb6d1e33c5adbad811.avif?t=1771935482\" width=902 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the RPX community as the game grows, and you might just get a <strong>free boat</strong>… or even find your name in the credits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/f15b405bbc554e9d1efdb93777b8e14f.poster.avif?t=1771935482\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/f15b405bbc554e9d1efdb93777b8e14f.webm?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337130/extras/f15b405bbc554e9d1efdb93777b8e14f.mp4?t=1771935482\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
